lastCommitMessage: Update agora_market_dart_sdk reference and enhance profile and avatar management features
- Updated agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference in pubspec.yaml and pubspec.lock to a new commit hash for consistency.
- Improved AuthService to handle profile updates with API responses, ensuring local storage is updated accordingly.
- Enhanced AvatarEditPage to automatically save uploaded avatars without requiring user confirmation.
- Updated ProfilePage to prioritize API avatar data and introduced a method for updating avatar URLs in local storage, improving user experience.
